{"tid":1008810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[純紀錄]  買利物浦贏11場中下游必勝奪冠 300上2100蚊 必賺7倍","createTime":"2019-02-04T17:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T14:43:02.000Z","uid":36238,"like":35,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ee784139608aebcc1f9afa847be46befb6c1bd2e","tid":1008810,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"仲有14場 睇好利記拎英超<br />\n對車獌熱有機會和波 就唔直屌主客<br />\n另外買 但係其他11場 平均都應該有1.2賠<br />\n贏硬既波諗唔到點解唔買 賺返個飯錢都好<br />\n7倍 風險低 回報高<br />\n<br />\n第一口 韋斯咸 對 利物浦<br />\n客勝 $300@1.25<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果推到第五口都順利 會double注碼<br />\n輸咗會抖一場 再推過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21db03877d89d58324ffa62c47f21ff2714060dc","tid":1008810,"uid":8500,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T17:57:50.000Z","msg":"都好既 破財擋災"},{"pid":"78c7c4188f1f05dd18c5ff0138f5668b2f03dfef","tid":1008810,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"照計1.25賠率推23口可以上五萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2382010346a12942b6ea434c55ab440a392521","tid":1008810,"uid":213699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78c7c4188f1f05dd18c5ff0138f5668b2f03dfef","tid":1008810,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T18:02:40.000Z","msg":"照計1.25賠率推23口可以上五萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T19:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfd2a6e5b77097669aec5eeac33c0c86f5bdae3","tid":1008810,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T21:57:55.000Z","msg":"Crash<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}